<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About - Badwolf Calisthenics</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/about.css" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Oswald:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- Firebase SDKs -->
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.0/firebase-app-compat.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.0/firebase-auth-compat.js"></script>

    <!-- Firebase Config -->
    <script src="js/firebase-config.js"></script>
    <script src="js/app.js" defer></script>
    <script src="js/carousel.js" defer></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
      <section class="about-text">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
      </section>
      <div class="carousel-container">
        <div class="about-carousel">
          <button class="carousel-btn prev">&#10094;</button>
          <img
            src="images/Room 2.jpg"
            alt="Slide 1"
            class="carousel-slide active"
          />
          <img
            src="images/Dumbbells 6.jpg"
            alt="Slide 2"
            class="carousel-slide"
          />
          <img
            src="images/Dumbbells 5.jpg"
            alt="Slide 3"
            class="carousel-slide"
          />
          <button class="carousel-btn next">&#10095;</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="about-text">
        <p>
          At Badwolf Calisthenics, we're passionate about unlocking the full
          potential of the human body through bodyweight strength, mobility, and
          endurance training. Whether you're a complete beginner or looking to
          advance your skill set, our structured coaching is built to help you
          move better, feel stronger, and train with purpose.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe in functional fitness that carries over into your daily
          life. Our sessions are supportive, challenging, and rooted in solid
          principles of progression. Join our community and start mastering your
          movement.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Badwolf Calisthenics. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
